<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>AlveoAir | Respiratory Support & Customer Guidance</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Respiratory support, equipment guidance, and customer service assistance for patients, caregivers, and respiratory equipment providers. English and Spanish support available.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="respiratory support, oxygen equipment help, CPAP support, nebulizer help, respiratory therapist, customer service, elderly respiratory care, oxygen concentrator support, English Spanish respiratory help">
  
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <div class="overlay">

    <!-- HERO / HEADER -->
    <header class="hero">
      <h1>AlveoAir</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Respiratory Support • Equipment Guidance • Customer Service</p>
    </header>

    <!-- TOP INTRO -->
    <section class="intro-card">
      <h2>Professional Respiratory Assistance in English & Español</h2>
      <p>
        With over 30 years of respiratory therapy experience, AlveoAir offers practical guidance
        for home respiratory equipment, customer support needs, and educational assistance for
        patients, families, and companies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- MAIN SPLIT SECTION -->
    <section class="split-layout">

      <!-- ENGLISH -->
      <div class="language-column left-column">
        <div class="lang-title">
          <h2>English</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>For Patients & Families</h3>
          <p>
            Help understanding oxygen equipment, nebulizers, CPAP/BiPAP devices, tubing, masks,
            humidifiers, alarms, and general respiratory supplies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>For Home Use Questions</h3>
          <p>
            Guidance when equipment is not working properly, needs replacement, or when you need
            help understanding what to do next.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>For Companies</h3>
          <p>
            Professional customer support assistance for respiratory and durable medical equipment
            providers seeking knowledgeable service and communication.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a href="en.html" class="btn">Enter English</a>
      </div>

      <!-- CENTER IMAGES -->
      <div class="image-column">
        <div class="image-stack">
          <img src="images/resp1.jpg" alt="Respiratory support consultation">
          <img src="images/resp2.jpg" alt="Home respiratory equipment guidance">
          <img src="images/resp3.jpg" alt="Professional respiratory care support">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SPANISH -->
      <div class="language-column right-column">
        <div class="lang-title">
          <h2>Español</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Para Pacientes y Familias</h3>
          <p>
            Ayuda para entender equipos de oxígeno, nebulizadores, CPAP/BiPAP, mangueras, mascarillas,
            humidificadores, alarmas y suministros respiratorios en casa.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Para Dudas del Equipo</h3>
          <p>
            Orientación cuando un equipo no funciona bien, necesita reemplazo o cuando usted necesita
            saber qué hacer después.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Para Empresas</h3>
          <p>
            Asistencia profesional en servicio al cliente para compañías de equipo respiratorio y
            equipo médico duradero que necesiten apoyo con experiencia.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a href="es.html" class="btn">Entrar en Español</a>
      </div>

    </section>

    <!-- BOTTOM MESSAGE -->
    <section class="bottom-card">
      <h2>Experience. Guidance. Confidence.</h2>
      <p>
        AlveoAir is designed to provide clear, respectful, and practical respiratory support guidance
        for everyday home equipment concerns and professional customer service needs.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer>
      <p>© 2026 AlveoAir.com • Respiratory Support Services</p>
    </footer>

